- "Prowess" is measured by the average score, which is calculated as the sum of the scores of both teams divided by two;
- "Vast arena of competitive gaming" is a metaphor for the database containing match and team information.

sql:
SELECT game_mode_name
FROM game_modes
WHERE game_mode_id = 0;

SELECT T1.map_name, T2.game_mode_name
FROM maps AS T1
INNER JOIN game_modes AS T2 ON T1.game_mode = T2.game_mode_name;

